<topic id="3f421301-4a9f-446a-b9e6-87adf8d2f850" revisionNumber="0">
  <developerConceptualDocument xmlns="http://ddue.schemas.microsoft.com/authoring/2003/5" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">
    <introduction>
      <para>
        This section contains a complete reference for all types and methods contained in SlimDX.
        Although they are not all completely documented at this point, we are working on rectifying
        this situation. If you need clarification on a certain method, see the corresponding entry
        in the DirectX SDK's documentation. The SlimDX methods closely match their DirectX counterparts.
      </para>
    </introduction>

    <section>
      <title>Namespaces</title>

      <content>
        <para>
          SlimDX is divided into the following namespaces:
        </para>
        <list class="bullet">
          <listItem>
            <para>
              <codeEntityReference>N:SlimDX</codeEntityReference>
              - Contains common classes and functionality not linked to a specific piece of DirectX, including the math library.
            </para>
          </listItem>
          <listItem>
            <para>
              <codeEntityReference>N:SlimDX.D3DCompiler</codeEntityReference>
              - Contains classes and types for Direct3D shader and effect compilation.
            </para>
          </listItem>
          <listItem>
            <para>
              <codeEntityReference>N:SlimDX.Design</codeEntityReference>
              - Contains classes to support design time functionality with SlimDX.
            </para>
          </listItem>
          <listItem>
            <para>
              <codeEntityReference>N:SlimDX.Direct2D</codeEntityReference>
              - Contains classes and types for Direct2D graphics support.
            </para>
          </listItem>
          <listItem>
            <para>
              <codeEntityReference>N:SlimDX.Direct3D10</codeEntityReference>
              - Contains classes and types for Direct3D 10 graphics support.
            </para>
          </listItem>
          <listItem>
            <para>
              <codeEntityReference>N:SlimDX.Direct3D10_1</codeEntityReference>
              - Contains classes and types for Direct3D 10.1 graphics support.
            </para>
          </listItem>
          <listItem>
            <para>
              <codeEntityReference>N:SlimDX.Direct3D11</codeEntityReference>
              - Contains classes and types for Direct3D 11 graphics support.
            </para>
          </listItem>
          <listItem>
            <para>
              <codeEntityReference>N:SlimDX.Direct3D9</codeEntityReference>
              - Contains classes and types for Direct3D 9 graphics support.
            </para>
          </listItem>
          <listItem>
            <para>
              <codeEntityReference>N:SlimDX.DirectInput</codeEntityReference>
              - Contains classes and types for DirectInput 8 support.
            </para>
          </listItem>
          <listItem>
            <para>
              <codeEntityReference>N:SlimDX.DirectSound</codeEntityReference>
              - Contains classes and types for DirectSound 8 support.
            </para>
          </listItem>
          <listItem>
            <para>
              <codeEntityReference>N:SlimDX.DirectWrite</codeEntityReference>
              - Contains classes and types for DirectWrite font and text support.
            </para>
          </listItem>
          <listItem>
            <para>
              <codeEntityReference>N:SlimDX.DXGI</codeEntityReference>
              - Contains classes and types for DXGI support.
            </para>
          </listItem>
          <listItem>
            <para>
              <codeEntityReference>N:SlimDX.Multimedia</codeEntityReference>
              - Contains classes and types for loading and processing multimedia files, such as sounds.
            </para>
          </listItem>
          <listItem>
            <para>
              <codeEntityReference>N:SlimDX.RawInput</codeEntityReference>
              - Contains classes and types for using the RawInput API.
            </para>
          </listItem>
          <listItem>
            <para>
              <codeEntityReference>N:SlimDX.Windows</codeEntityReference>
              - Contains classes and types for various bits of Win32 functionality.
            </para>
          </listItem>
          <listItem>
            <para>
              <codeEntityReference>N:SlimDX.X3DAudio</codeEntityReference>
              - Contains classes and types for X3D Audio support.
            </para>
          </listItem>
          <listItem>
            <para>
              <codeEntityReference>N:SlimDX.XACT3</codeEntityReference>
              - Contains classes and types for the cross platform audio content library (XACT).
            </para>
          </listItem>
          <listItem>
            <para>
              <codeEntityReference>N:SlimDX.XAPO</codeEntityReference>
              - Contains classes and types for the cross platform audio processing object library (XAPO).
            </para>
          </listItem>
          <listItem>
            <para>
              <codeEntityReference>N:SlimDX.XAudio2</codeEntityReference>
              - Contains classes and types for XAudio 2 support.
            </para>
          </listItem>
          <listItem>
            <para>
              <codeEntityReference>N:SlimDX.XInput</codeEntityReference>
              - Contains classes and types for XInput support.
            </para>
          </listItem>
        </list>
      </content>
    </section>
  </developerConceptualDocument>
</topic>